Comandos:

Agregar los repositorios de docker:

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install apt-transport-https ca-certificates curl software-properties-common
curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo apt-key add -
sudo add-apt-repository "deb [arch=amd64] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu $(lsb_release -cs) stable"

Instalaci√≥n de docker-ce:

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install docker-ce

Instalar Docker-Compose:

sudo curl -L "https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.23.2/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m)" -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose
sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose

Descargar e instalar laradock:

git clone https://github.com/Laradock/laradock.git
cd laradock
cp env-example .env
sudo docker-compose up -d nginx

Instalar el proyecto:

sudo docker-compose exec workspace bash
git clone https://github.com/L4rmand0/DRAIV.git
exit

Instalar el composer:


Arreglar el composer update:

sudo /bin/dd if=/dev/zero of=/var/swap.1 bs=1M count=1024
sudo /sbin/mkswap /var/swap.1
sudo /sbin/swapon /var/swap.1

composer require aws/aws-sdk-php

sudo chown -R $USER $HOME/.composer
sudo apt install php-cli composer unzip

sudo apt-get install -y php7.2-gd
sudo apt-get install php7.2-intl
sudo apt-get install php7.2-xsl
sudo apt-get install php7.2-xml
sudo apt-get install php7.2-mbstring
composer require aws/aws-sdk-php
composer update
chmod 777 -R /home/ubuntu/DRAIV/


